{
  "stem": "20088.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I took as well some [? eiderdowns, ?] which I still have, which, you know, which came from transport.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was stored.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I took some big leather boots, which I had for a long time till Odessa when I swapped it for a chicken.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And anyway, we got water from this pond, and we-- it was icy cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But then later, we found in this-- those barracks where the SS lived, there was a stove and wood, and we could cook.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then my-- my mother and a Polish woman and a French girl decided we would leave the camp and live in this barrack, the four of us, because it was terrible in that hospital block.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Another thing which still happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There were still a few people who could walk, and most people were dying every day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And one day an older woman called me and she said, come here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We need you to carry a body out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I said, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I can't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I can't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And so my mother was still in her bed, and she said, I'll come down and carry that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But she didn't have the strength to carry, so we together carried.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And there was outside the blocks, it was-- everything was frozen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We just heaped the bodies up, and it was, you know, it was-- it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "All stiff and frozen and-- But it was beautiful weather.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was everything was in snow and blue sky.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the sun shone on this-- you know, it-- it just didn't fit together at all, this image.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But I will still remember this beautiful, sparkling, diamond snow and just all those bodies heaped in a corner.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
